HomePage.subtitle: Capture your favorite memories with your own, one-of-one phone case. CaseCobra allows you to protect your memories, not just your phone case.

customerssay.title: What our customers say
customerssay.customerOne: The case feels durable and I even got a compliment on the design. Had the case for two and a half months now and the image is super clear , on the case I had before, the image started fading into yellow-ish color after a couple weeks. Love it.
customerssay.customerTwo: I usually keep my phone together with my keys in my pocket and that led to some pretty heavy scratchmarks on all of my last phone cases. This one, besides a barely noticeable scratch on the corner, looks brand new after about half a year . I dig it.
